OL,6,FA cannabis grower tried to evade
OL,7,Fpolice by hiding behind a curtain.
OL,9,FRonaldo Sela, 26, was arrested when
OL,10,Fofficers forced their way into a
OL,11,Fdisused shop on , on 13 December last
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FMore than were found inside two
OL,15,Fseparate rooms that had been rigged as
OL,16,Fpart of what police described as "an
OL,17,Factive grow'.
OL,19,FThey were being powered on a 24-hour
OL,20,Ftimer using more than 40 separate
OL,21,Flights and 39 electrical transformers.
