OL,6,FSergeant Chris Gifford, of Stoke-on-
OL,7,FTrent North local policing team, said:
OL,8,F"We want to make it clear that drug
OL,9,Fcultivation in Staffordshire will not
OL,10,Fbe tolerated.
OL,12,F"These grows are often run by
OL,13,Fsophisticated criminal groups who
OL,14,Fprofit from careers in crime.
OL,16,F"They steal electric, set-up dangerous
OL,17,Frigs that are significant fire safety
OL,18,Fhazards and blight vulnerable people
OL,19,Fin local communities.
